data.description: Looking for a well built home to add your personal touches? The owners have enjoyed this 2 bedroom 2 bath home in the Piedmont neighborhood for almost 30 years.  The kitchen offers plenty of natural light with two garden windows facing the backyard.  The dining area has a patio door that leads to the back yard deck.  Original hardwood floors in the bedrooms are ready for a refresh.  The living room gives you plenty of space for family and friends.  The lower level is a walk out basement & offers tons of opportunity for additional living space with a family room, a laundry area, a ¾ bath and a perfect space for a workshop.  The spacious fenced in backyard has beautiful trees and gardening opportunities. The 24’ x 32’ garage adds to the convenience and includes a 220 outlet. A great opportunity to build equity.  Schedule your private showing today.
